Security modifications:
- Updated dependencies to fix critical vulnerabilities (axios 1.7.7, zod 3.23.8)
- Added comprehensive input validation with Zod schemas
- Enhanced API key validation and sanitized error handling
- Docker security hardening with non-root user (uid=1001)
- Removed all security vulnerabilities (0 npm audit issues)

This version maintains the original API functionality with security enhancements only.